  "bodyHtml": "<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Танд дөрвөлжин шугамтай&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Span-3\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-style: italic;\">M</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-4\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.219em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">×</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-5\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.219em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-style: italic;\">N</span>&nbsp;хэмжээтэй тэгш өнцөгт самбар болон&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Span-8\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">2</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-9\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.219em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">×</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-10\" style=\"color: black; line-height: normal; white-space: nowrap; word-spacing: normal; transition: none; -webkit-transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.219em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">1</span>&nbsp;хэмжээтэй төгсгөлгүй олон даалуунууд өгөгдсөн. Даалууг эргүүлж болно. Даалууг самбар дээр байрлуулахдаа дараах дүрмүүдийг дагана:</span></p>\n<ol style=\"margin: 0.5em 0px 0px 1em; padding: 0px; list-style-position: outside; list-style-image: initial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 21px; color: #222222; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\">\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Даалуу бүр яг хоёр дөрвөлжинг халхлана.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Аль ч хоёр даалуу давхардаж байрлахгүй.</span></li>\n<li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 0.8em; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.5em;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Даалуу самбараас халихгүй дотор нь байрлана.</span></li>\n</ol>\n<p style=\"margin: 1.5em 0px 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 1.4em; color: #222222;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Тийм бол байрлуулж болох даалууны хамгийн их утгыг ол.</span></p>\n<h3>Input</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">Нэг мөрөнд самбарын хэмжээг илтгэх</span><span style=\"color: #222222;\">&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 19.600000381469727px; font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">M</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">,&nbsp;<span style=\"font-style: italic; white-space: nowrap; color: #000000;\">N</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">&nbsp;(&nbsp;<span id=\"MathJax-Span-19\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">1</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-20\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-21\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-style: italic;\">M</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-22\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-23\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px; font-style: italic;\">N</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-24\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">≤</span><span id=\"MathJax-Span-25\" style=\"white-space: nowrap; color: #000000; -webkit-transition: none; transition: none; display: inline; position: static; border: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 0.273em; margin: 0px; vertical-align: 0px;\">16</span></span><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\">) хоёр тоо байна.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Output</h3>\n<p><span style=\"color: #222222; line-height: 19.600000381469727px;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">Хариу болох ганц тоо.</span></span></p>\n<h3>Example</h3>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 1:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">2 4</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"> <strong>Output 1:</strong> </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Input 2:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">3 3</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>Output 2:</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: small;\">4</span></p>",
  "bodyText": "Танд дөрвөлжин шугамтай M×N хэмжээтэй тэгш өнцөгт самбар болон 2×1 хэмжээтэй төгсгөлгүй олон даалуунууд өгөгдсөн. Даалууг эргүүлж болно. Даалууг самбар дээр байрлуулахдаа дараах дүрмүүдийг дагана:\n\nДаалуу бүр яг хоёр дөрвөлжинг халхлана.\nАль ч хоёр даалуу давхардаж байрлахгүй.\nДаалуу самбараас халихгүй дотор нь байрлана.\n\nТийм бол байрлуулж болох даалууны хамгийн их утгыг ол.\nInput\nНэг мөрөнд самбарын хэмжээг илтгэх M, N ( 1≤M≤N≤16) хоёр тоо байна.\nOutput\nХариу болох ганц тоо.\nExample\nInput 1: \n2 4\n Output 1: \n4\nInput 2:\n3 3\nOutput 2:\n4",
